Long Realty Covey Luxury Properties - Main

data.description: Nestled on a spacious .60-acre lot, this home has a newly remodeled kitchen, 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, w/ the flexibility of converting the office space into a potential 4th bedroom. New metal roof. Custom chain link privacy fence surrounds the back lot. The highlight of the backyard is the 40X 40 garage w/ 16- foot walls & an RV door (12X8 Ft) to keep your RV out of the weather. Additionally, a 10X12 shed provides extra storage space, & an open back lot for more space, propane tank is owned. The inviting jacuzzi offering a perfect spot for relaxation & enjoying the beautiful sunsets in this area. Outdoor enthusiasts will revel in the location, w/ the USFS all around, offering trails for ATVs & exploration galore. The TV & mount, and rolling kitchen island, does not convey.
